    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty handles perfectly and looks great doing it. It's super reliable and looking for a new home\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
