    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's analog peak, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with precision, including a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. It features a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup with refreshed bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the high-strung performance and mechanical harmony expected of the M-division's most iconic platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
