    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a prime example of a well-maintained luxury SUV that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finished in Eminent White Pearl retains a brilliant luster, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. Inside, the parchment leather interior is remarkably clean; the seats remain firm and supportive, showing only slight natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the heated/ventilated seats, navigation system, and power liftgate, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound, having followed a strict synthetic oil change schedule every 5,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last season. It drives straight and quiet, offering that signature Lexus smoothness without any rattles or unexpected vibrations.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
